ygData.messageBody:
Well me and my friend was in South Karana by ourselves and doing fine. We
are now headed to Unrest to see what we can do, but I'd say we'll be in a
bigger team or we won't make it in there long. I'd say if we get killed a
few times we're outta there for a while. I know have me an Ruined Totem
Staff and a friend told me he'd try to get me an Glowing Wooden Crook soon.

**************************
Azor
Lvl 18 Human Cleric of the Rathe
**************************
